{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.twilio","typeVersion":1,"position":[3861,1420],"id":"36e07585-6fc4-4985-8531-82a5e55583a9","name":"Escalate Failure to Twilio","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Receive Inbound Webhook\n\nEntry point: listens for POST calls on `/wf00326-request`. Use the TEST url while building, switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Read Recent from Airtable","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"95921f85-9cd3-96dd-90a0-b7f1d94b3d50","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Read Recent from Airtable\n\nairtable — `search` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Newest First · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"e3f06e4c-2702-8439-7a90-7972ded3f66a","name":"Note: Read Recent from Airtable"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Trim to Digest Size","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"2c775a8d-b061-eb34-bee1-de0ebe5594c2","name":"Note: Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Trim to Digest Size\n\nCaps the stream at 15 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Summarize Content (AI)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"2cde6acd-1d50-f498-c3b3-06424dbdc64c","name":"Note: Trim to Digest Size"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Content (AI)\n\nMap-reduce summarization chain — handles long content without blowing the context window.\n\nPorts: ①→ Render as HTML · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"e958f307-dc6c-7a7e-f0b9-5fd2157ba40e","name":"Note: Summarize Content (AI)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### OpenAI Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `gpt-4o-mini`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Summarize Content (AI)** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenAI API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,1090],"id":"b20468f6-38c8-61fb-0d43-8618521a9235","name":"Note: OpenAI Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Render as HTML\n\nConverts markdown to HTML for rich rendering in email/CMS.\n\nNext: Post Digest to Twilio","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,520],"id":"372d3bbe-d06b-4a43-ae29-92cc793634a8","name":"Note: Render as HTML"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Post Digest to Twilio\n\ntwilio — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Archive Digest in Airtable · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Twilio SID + token","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1857,520],"id":"bd9f24b7-9246-5ae4-08af-5ac4298c3d6e","name":"Note: Post Digest to Twilio"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Digest in Airtable\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Align Field Names · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2181,520],"id":"1e2d288c-6906-00e5-411d-75eca9431d97","name":"Note: Archive Digest in Airtable"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2505,520],"id":"c0b1c2d4-ffc4-8105-b091-076d52fa26ae","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Sort Requests Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2829,520],"id":"28ae8e6b-e567-babd-828d-7569a73fcc4d","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Requests Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3153,520],"id":"cc4ff478-b669-f3fc-205b-6d0e6d690146","name":"Note: Sort Requests Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Airtable)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3477,520],"id":"c956d506-78ae-4b0a-28ca-59fc6ec0dc88","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Airtable)\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Twilio · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,520],"id":"5997835f-3aef-7267-ec56-a091a33b3311","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Airtable)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Twilio\n\ntwilio — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Twilio SID + token","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,520],"id":"6606a8dc-aff1-edd4-abbe-128e29438b4c","name":"Note: Send Summary to Twilio"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Twilio","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3477,1540],"id":"fe1fae24-5148-a1dc-31dc-eedf176ab3d0","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Twilio\n\ntwilio — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Twilio SID + token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,1540],"id":"6ec4cf26-1108-6758-c5c2-b06fae4d433a","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Twilio"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Digest documents with Airtable and Twilio\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nDigest documents with Airtable and Twilio. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual multi-tool agent is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Read Recent from Airtable → Newest First → Trim to Digest Size → Summarize Content (AI) → Render as HTML → Post Digest to Twilio → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating multi-tool agent in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Standardizes the process every time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Airtable PAT; OpenAI API key; Twilio SID + token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"3baf8b16-3d30-5dfe-715d-db830268582b","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"1a61590b-5b61-ac43-4e60-90d0272c4a32","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"f4688c3f-d582-1b09-7125-cd879b715646","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"2406e77a-f212-94ee-6cc7-18c8eb835509","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your multi-tool agent process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-20],"id":"1d7d551d-eb97-ac1c-76d7-74cf0557ed58","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Read Recent from Airtable","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Read Recent from Airtable":{"main":[[{"node":"Newest First","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Trim to Digest Size","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Trim to Digest Size":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Content (AI)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenAI Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Summarize Content (AI)","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Summarize Content (AI)":{"main":[[{"node":"Render as HTML","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Render as HTML":{"main":[[{"node":"Post Digest to Twilio","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Post Digest to Twilio":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Digest in Airtable","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Digest in Airtable":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Requests Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Requests Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Airtable)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Airtable)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Twilio","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Twilio","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Twilio":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"df825bff-f43d-438f-9a79-37ef9c987463","id":"FDX00326"}